<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ش ط أ:</span> <span class="c2">(شَطْءُ)</span> الزَّرْعِ وَالنَّبَاتِ فِرَاخُهُ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ الْأَخْفَشُ:</span> طَرَفُهُ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(أَشْطَأَ)</span> الزَّرْعُ خَرَجَ <span class="c2">(شَطْؤُهُ)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">⦗١٦٥⦘ وَشَاطِئُ الْوَادِي شَطُّهُ وَجَانِبُهُ وَيُقَالُ:</span> <span class="c2">(شَاطِئُ)</span> الْأَوْدِيَةِ وَلَا يُجْمَعُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>